{{Lunisolar October}} 
'''October 2''' is the 2nd day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=Kannazuki|1=Kannazuki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Keikō Tennō|ja|景行天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 40th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|110|ja|110|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が東夷討伐に出発
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1855|ja|1855|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 11|ja|11月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The {{ill|Ansei Edo Earthquake|ja|安政江戸Earthquake|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  struck, causing heavy damage primarily in downtown areas with over 7,000 fatalities.
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1870|ja|1870|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The Meiji government established a policy that the army adopt French methods and the navy British methods.

== Births ==
