* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 20th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1643|ja|1643|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tenkai|ja|天海|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Tendai monk (* {{ill|1536|ja|1536|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
