'''October 2''' is the 2nd day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=Kannazuki|1=Kannazuki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Keikō Tennō|ja|景行天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 40th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|110|ja|110|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が東夷討伐に出発
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1855|ja|1855|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 11|ja|11月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The {{ill|Ansei Edo Earthquake|ja|安政江戸Earthquake|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  struck, causing heavy damage primarily in downtown areas with over 7,000 fatalities.
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1870|ja|1870|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The Meiji government established a policy that the army adopt French methods and the navy British methods.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Hōreki|ja|Hōreki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1758|ja|1758|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Ryōkan|ja|良寛|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Sōtō Zen monk, poet, and calligrapher († {{ill|1831|ja|1831|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Hōki|ja|宝亀|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|775|ja|775|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Kibi Shinbi|ja|吉備真備|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a sinologist and court official (* {{ill|693|ja|693|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Tenbun (era)|ja|天文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 22nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1553|ja|1553|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 7|ja|11月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Yamazaki Sōkan|ja|山崎宗鑑|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a renka master and haiku poet (* {{ill|1465|ja|1465|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 20th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1643|ja|1643|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 13|ja|11月13日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tenkai|ja|天海|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Tendai monk (* {{ill|1536|ja|1536|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1835|ja|1835|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 21|ja|11月21日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Kawaoka Seishū|ja|華岡青洲|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a physician and pioneer of anesthesia (* {{ill|1760|ja|1760|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|1855|ja|1855|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 11|ja|11月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Fujita Tōko|ja|藤田東湖|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a Confucian scholar (* {{ill|1806|ja|1806|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).

