{{Lunisolar October}} 
'''October 2''' is the 2nd day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜}}  day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Keikō Tennō|ja|景行天皇}} 40th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}}  {{ill|110|ja|110}}  {{ill|November 1|ja|11月1日}} ） – {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル}} が東夷討伐に出発
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1855|ja|1855}}  {{ill|November 11|ja|11月11日}} ） – The {{ill|Ansei Edo Earthquake|ja|安政江戸Earthquake}}  struck, causing heavy damage primarily in downtown areas with over 7,000 fatalities.
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}}  {{ill|1870|ja|1870}}  {{ill|October 26|ja|10月26日}} ） – The Meiji government established a policy that the army adopt French methods and the navy British methods.

== Births ==
