* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|1855|ja|1855|qq=|12=draft}}  {{ill|November 11|ja|11月11日|qq=|12=draft}} ） – The {{ill|Ansei Edo Earthquake|ja|安政江戸Earthquake|qq=|12=draft}}  struck, causing heavy damage primarily in downtown areas with over 7,000 fatalities.
