{{Not to be confused with|October 2 (Lunisolar)}}<!--hatnote--> {{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十月初二|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 10월 2일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar October|qq=}} '''October 2''' is the 2nd day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October (Lunisolar)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannazuki|qq=}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taian|qq=}} .
== Events == * [[:en:Emperor Keikō|Keikō Tennō]] 40th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:110 (number)|110]] [[:en:November 1|November 1]] ） – {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|qq=}} が東夷討伐に出発 * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 2nd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1855|ja|1855|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1855|qq=}} [[:en:November 11|November 11]] ） – The {{ill|Ansei Edo Earthquake|ja|安政江戸Earthquake|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei Edo Earthquake|qq=}} struck, causing heavy damage primarily in downtown areas with over 7,000 fatalities. * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 3rd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1870|ja|1870|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1870|qq=}} [[:en:October 26|October 26]] ） – The Meiji government established a policy that the army adopt French methods and the navy British methods.
== Births == * {{ill|Hōreki|1=Hōreki|2=ja|3=宝暦|ja|Hōreki|1=Hōreki|2=ja|3=宝暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hōreki|qq=}} 8th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1758|ja|1758|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1758|qq=}} [[:en:November 2|November 2]] ） – [[:en:Ryōkan|Ryōkan]] , a Sōtō Zen monk, poet, and calligrapher († {{ill|1831|ja|1831|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1831|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Hōki|Hōki]] 6th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|775|ja|775|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/775|qq=}} [[:en:October 30|October 30]] ） – [[:en:Kibi no Makibi|Kibi Shinbi]] , a sinologist and court official (* [[:en:693 (number)|693]] ). * {{ill|Tenbun (era)|ja|天文|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenbun (era)|qq=}} 22nd year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|1553|ja|1553|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1553|qq=}} [[:en:November 7|November 7]] ） – [[:en:Yamazaki Sōkan|Yamazaki Sōkan]] , a renka master and haiku poet (* {{ill|1465|ja|1465|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1465|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] 20th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1643|ja|1643|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1643|qq=}} [[:en:November 13|November 13]] ） – [[:en:Tenkai|Tenkai]] , a Tendai monk (* {{ill|1536|ja|1536|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1536|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 6th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1835|ja|1835|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1835|qq=}} [[:en:November 21|November 21]] ） – [[:en:Hanaoka Seishū|Kawaoka Seishū]] , a physician and pioneer of anesthesia (* {{ill|1760|ja|1760|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1760|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 2nd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1855|ja|1855|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1855|qq=}} [[:en:November 11|November 11]] ） – [[:en:Fujita Tōko|Fujita Tōko]] , a Confucian scholar (* {{ill|1806|ja|1806|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1806|qq=}} ).
