== Events == * [[:en:Emperor Keikō|Keikō Tennō]] 40th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:110|110]] [[:en:November 1|November 1]] ） – {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to ヤマトタケル}} が東夷討伐に出発 * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 2nd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1855|ja|1855|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1855|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 11|November 11]] ） – The {{ill|Ansei Edo Earthquake|ja|安政江戸Earthquake|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei Edo Earthquake|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} struck, causing heavy damage primarily in downtown areas with over 7,000 fatalities. * [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]] 3rd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1870|ja|1870|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1870|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:October 26|October 26]] ） – The Meiji government established a policy that the army adopt French methods and the navy British methods.
== Births == * [[:en:Hōreki|Hōreki]] 8th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1758|1758]] [[:en:November 2|November 2]] ） – [[:en:Ryōkan|Ryōkan]] , a Sōtō Zen monk, poet, and calligrapher († [[:en:1831|1831]] ).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Hōki|Hōki]] 6th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] {{ill|775|ja|775|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/775|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 700}} [[:en:October 30|October 30]] ） – [[:en:Kibi no Makibi|Kibi Shinbi]] , a sinologist and court official (* [[:en:693|693]] ). * {{ill|Tenbun (era)|ja|天文|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenbun (era)|qq=}} 22nd year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1553|1553]] [[:en:November 7|November 7]] ） – [[:en:Yamazaki Sōkan|Yamazaki Sōkan]] , a renka master and haiku poet (* [[:en:1465|1465]] ). * [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] 20th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1643|1643]] [[:en:November 13|November 13]] ） – [[:en:Tenkai|Tenkai]] , a Tendai monk (* [[:en:1536|1536]] ). * [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] 6th year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1835|ja|1835|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1835|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 21|November 21]] ） – [[:en:Hanaoka Seishū|Kawaoka Seishū]] , a physician and pioneer of anesthesia (* [[:en:1760|1760]] ). * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 2nd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1855|ja|1855|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1855|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} [[:en:November 11|November 11]] ） – [[:en:Fujita Tōko|Fujita Tōko]] , a Confucian scholar (* [[:en:1806|1806]] ).
