'''October 2''' is the 2nd day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/October (Lunisolar)|13=User:Immanuelle/Kannazuki|comment=enwiki is a redirect}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}}  day is {{ill|Taian|WD=Q96759844|1=taian}}{{efn|ja|大安|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taian|1=taian|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q1306255}} .

== Events ==
* {{ill|Emperor Keikō|en|Emperor Keikō|WD=Q329723|lt=Keikō Tennō|1=Emperor Keikō}} 40th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}}  {{ill|110|en|110|WD=Q170338|lt=110|1=110}}  {{ill|November 1|en|November 1|WD=Q2997|lt=November 1|1=November 1}} ） – {{ill|Yamato Takeru|ja|日本武尊|1=Yamato Takeru|lt=Prince Yamato Takeru|3=ヤマトタケル|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|13=User:Immanuelle/Yamato Takeru|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to ヤマトタケル|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q461258}} が東夷討伐に出発
* {{ill|Ansei|en|Ansei|WD=Q1327259|lt=Ansei|1=Ansei}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}}  {{ill|1855|en|1855|WD=Q7673|lt=1855|1=1855}}  {{ill|November 11|en|November 11|WD=Q2987|lt=November 11|1=November 11}} ） – The {{ill|Ansei Edo Earthquake|ja|安政江戸Earthquake|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei Edo Earthquake|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}  struck, causing heavy damage primarily in downtown areas with over 7,000 fatalities.
* {{ill|Meiji era|en|Meiji era|WD=Q3125096|lt=Meiji era|1=Meiji era}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}}  {{ill|1870|en|1870|WD=Q7741|lt=1870|1=1870}}  {{ill|October 26|en|October 26|WD=Q2953|lt=October 26|1=October 26}} ） – The Meiji government established a policy that the army adopt French methods and the navy British methods.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Hōreki|en|Hōreki|WD=Q1194397|lt=Hōreki|1=Hōreki}} 8th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}}  {{ill|1758|en|1758|WD=Q7639|lt=1758|1=1758}}  {{ill|November 2|en|November 2|WD=Q2996|lt=November 2|1=November 2}} ） – {{ill|Ryōkan|en|Ryōkan|WD=Q5338269|lt=Ryōkan|1=Ryōkan}} , a Sōtō Zen monk, poet, and calligrapher († {{ill|1831|en|1831|WD=Q7579|lt=1831|1=1831}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Hōki|en|Hōki|WD=Q18520676|lt=Hōki|1=Hōki}} 6th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}}  {{ill|775|en|775|WD=Q30075|lt=775|1=775}}  {{ill|October 30|en|October 30|WD=Q2950|lt=October 30|1=October 30}} ） – {{ill|Kibi no Makibi|en|Kibi no Makibi|WD=Q1063276|lt=Kibi Shinbi|1=Kibi no Makibi}} , a sinologist and court official (* {{ill|693|en|693|WD=Q23480|lt=693|1=693}} ).
* {{ill|Tenbun (era)|ja|天文|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenbun (era)|1=Tenmon|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q21096812}} 22nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}}  {{ill|1553|en|1553|WD=Q6568|lt=1553|1=1553}}  {{ill|November 7|en|November 7|WD=Q2989|lt=November 7|1=November 7}} ） – {{ill|Yamazaki Sōkan|en|Yamazaki Sōkan|WD=Q860563|lt=Yamazaki Sōkan|1=Yamazaki Sōkan}} , a renka master and haiku poet (* {{ill|1465|en|1465|WD=Q6556|lt=1465|1=1465}} ).
* {{ill|Kan'ei|en|Kan'ei|WD=Q1192913|lt=Kan'ei|1=Kan'ei}} 20th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}}  {{ill|1643|en|1643|WD=Q6917|lt=1643|1=1643}}  {{ill|November 13|en|November 13|WD=Q2984|lt=November 13|1=November 13}} ） – {{ill|Tenkai|en|Tenkai|WD=Q1142310|lt=Tenkai|1=Tenkai}} , a Tendai monk (* {{ill|1536|en|1536|WD=Q6457|lt=1536|1=1536}} ).
* {{ill|Tenpō|en|Tenpō|WD=Q1369045|lt=Tenpō|1=Tenpō}} 6th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}}  {{ill|1835|en|1835|WD=Q7597|lt=1835|1=1835}}  {{ill|November 21|en|November 21|WD=Q3023|lt=November 21|1=November 21}} ） – {{ill|Hanaoka Seishū|en|Hanaoka Seishū|WD=Q1376935|lt=Kawaoka Seishū|1=Hanaoka Seishū}} , a physician and pioneer of anesthesia (* {{ill|1760|en|1760|WD=Q7646|lt=1760|1=1760}} ).
* {{ill|Ansei|en|Ansei|WD=Q1327259|lt=Ansei|1=Ansei}} 2nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}}  {{ill|1855|en|1855|WD=Q7673|lt=1855|1=1855}}  {{ill|November 11|en|November 11|WD=Q2987|lt=November 11|1=November 11}} ） – {{ill|Fujita Tōko|en|Fujita Tōko|WD=Q6564466|lt=Fujita Tōko|1=Fujita Tōko}} , a Confucian scholar (* {{ill|1806|en|1806|WD=Q6903|lt=1806|1=1806}} ).

